		gap: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem 2rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 0 0 0.75rem 0.75rem;
	}

	.socials {
		z-index: 15;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		gap: 2rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
